{
  "stem": "13817.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He promised them the world, and they went for him and voted for him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He-- everybody knows about the burning of the Reichstag there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He blamed the Communists for doing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He did it-- his-- his hordes did it themselves just to get the sympathy and to get everybody in line.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then in beginning of, I think, March or April, around this time, they started boycotting Jewish businesses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There would be one in a brown shirt would stand in front of the business and would say, don't buy here because it's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They would write Jew on the-- on the show window with a-- with a star of David.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was actually the beginning of-- of the-- that you would feel the Nazi deal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But even in this little town, people would-- lots of people would ignore it and the business still was going quite well.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We still had six, seven, or eight-- maybe eight employees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And until about I would say beginning of '38, middle of '37, our business wasn't that much affected.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My brother was an apprentice in-- in-- in Cologne and not in the business itself because my mother didn't want him to be the boss over the-- over the employees.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then in '34 after I was kicked out of school, I went also into apprenticeship in plumbing in-- in Cologne which involved a-- a train ride where you had to transfer a couple of times of about an hour or less, a little less.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And even on that train ride, a lot of boys or friends would still talk to me, sit with me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we would play cards to-- to keep busy to get there.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
